revenue recognition we derive our revenue from three sources i product revenue  which includes license fees for products sold as software or on appliances  subscription based license fees  and transaction based license fees  ii service revenue  which includes support and maintenance fees  consulting fees  and training fees  and iii intellectual property and other revenue which includes patent license agreement fees and the sale of distribution rights 
